snippet.title: Welcome
snippet.description:
Introduction video for Kotlin. 
Stay tuned for whole series of Kotlin Tutorials.
Kotlin has been declared as a first language of android.
But this doesn't mean Java is no more in picture. Kotlin has been added to the languages used in android , it has not replaced it. 
I would recommend beginners for android to start coding with kotlin because future jobs would be more  based on kotlin.
Current version of Kotlin - 1.1.2/April 25, 2017

Complete Series : https://goo.gl/UvHW5S

Official website for Kotlin : kotlinlang.org

Pre-requisites for the course : Core Java Basics

snippet.description:
